Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克 這麼晚你到哪裏野去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她擔心你 出去找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…出去了 她出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克怎麼了 你好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
